data.description: LOVELY BRICK HOME OFFERED FOR SALE IN THE DOWNTOWN DISTRICT OF LAFAYETTE, GA!  THIS ICONIC HOME SITS ON A BEAUTIFUL 1.6+ ACRE LOT OFFERING A NICE LEVEL YARD, CIRCULAR DR, RELAXING COURTYARD & CARPORT IN THE BACK AREA OF THE PROPERTY, AND 2 STORAGE BUILDINGS.  STEPPING INSIDE YOU WILL FIND A LOVELY FOYER FEATURING A GRAND STAIRWAY AND GLEAMING HARDWOODS THROUGHOUT HOME, TO THE RIGHT OF THE FOYER YOU WILL FIND A SPACIOUS LIVING ROOM, DINING ROOM WITH THE KITCHEN TUCKED QUIETLY IN THE BACK OF HOME. TO THE LEFT OF THE FOYER, YOU WILL FIND A GUEST BR W/BATH, LAUNDRY ROOM & MASTER BR W/BATH...THIS LOVELY FLOOR PLAN IS JOINED ON THE BACKSIDE OF HOME WITH A COZY DEN THAT FEATURES A WOOD BURNING FIREPLACE THAT STEPS OUT TO THE COURTYARD!  UPSTAIRS YOU WILL FIND 2 ADDITIONAL BEDROOMS W/OPPORTUNITY FOR AN ADDITIONAL STUDY AREA/STORAGE AND BATH.  THIS HOME IS FULL OF PERSONALITY OFFERING ORIGINAL WOODEN ACCENTS THROUGHOUT HOME...IT IS A RARE FIND!  CALL FOR YOUR PRIVATE SHOWING!  LOCATED LESS THAN 30 MINS FROM CHATTANOOGA/2 HRS FROM ATLANTA OR BIRMINGHAM!
